Average word length (/words/avg_len)
Tokenization - all words are alphabetical and can include apostrophes, but apostrophes do not count towards the length

Most common word (/words/most_com)
As is

Find the word(s) with the median frequency in the corpus (/words/median)
I sorted the frequency distribution alphabetically so when there are words with the same frequency at the median, I return what is at the median sorted alphabetically

Average sentence length (/sentences/avg_len)
A sentence is anything length of text ending in a . or ? or !

Find all phone numbers (/phones)
Takes in formats such as:
123-456-7890
(123)-456-7890
1234567890

Hosted on Heroku - https://mark43.herokuapp.com/